{
  "stem": "13851.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in-- at the beginning-- beginning of 1944, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] or maybe before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's hard to remember the years, but it was-- it-- it was-- oh, maybe the end of summer 1943.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was when they liquidated Blizyn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Couldn't tell, because they have-- they have dates when it was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I found out all the dates where it was-- from on-- from on the camp [INAUDIBLE] when they liquidated people, they found out from archives that when it happened.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On train, we were quite a few hours and all packed like sardines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was no food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No drinks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this was just a few hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I arrived in Birkenau, and they opened the-- opened the trains.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the SS with-- with-- with the dogs, screaming, and they-- and they-- they took us from Blizyn-- I think they took us for work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They assumed that we worked in Blizyn that we gonna work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I don't know if they took the whole transport for work or not, but mostly other transport came, right away they didn't-- they didn't take them to work.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just sent them to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we were assigned to work, but there was nothing work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We just cleaned Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There wasn't a factory to work for people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It just was a waiting station to be sent to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, what-- what we remember there was appells.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told you about appells, putting appells, counting to make sure that there-- there's nobody disappeared.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Appell is something-- all from the barracks at a certain time in the evening or in the morning, was do twice.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the morning out and the evening, to count every-- to count everyone is there.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
